author: @BiancaAguglia
text: Good explanation, Krish.  I too like the Springboard channel. It is a nice complement to channels like yours. It shows interviews with some smart and experienced data scientists who talk about the way their teams work, the kind of projects they work on, etc. Those interviews make it easier to see how the things you teach in your videos are used to solve real problems.
